cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL. 

The paper proposes a novel training method for improving confidence calibration of deep neural networks (DNNs) for classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves training a confidence model jointly with the classification model, which suggests the possibility of it belonging to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on multiple datasets, which indicates the possibility of it belonging to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
